{"tid":2130844,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"窮撚咪撚害自己嘅下一代","createTime":"2020-07-29T12:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T12:33:45.000Z","uid":312126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0bfe652158017bdd8d31a0a253a469a99f42709d","tid":2130844,"uid":312126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iVkzvQY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiVkzvQY.jpg&h=4f00a66b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢排最近成日係屋企嘈<br />\n我就成日覺得冇咩窮人上到大學<br />\n跟住專登揾下啲數據 結果如我所料<br />\nummm好正常嘅 <br />\n基層家庭係學習時期嘅洗費/支出都唔夠<br />\n啲學生要用時間翻pt 少左時間温書 <br />\n甚至對翻學失去左興趣<br />\n有幾多個細路係基層家庭上kongu呢<br />\n<br />\n我的確都有段時間係對翻學冇左興趣<br />\n當然自已都有懶惰嘅因素<br />\n令到自已唔交功課<br />\n因為個陣我覺得錢重要過任何嘢<br />\n中一二個陣一個星期得50蚊車費錢 <br />\n而我一日撘車都要九個幾<br />\n搞到要12歲到14歲就打啲on9工<br />\n啲搬單車 臨記 裝修嘅清潔 荼餐廳樓雜 <br />\n大部分都係最低工資<br />\n一到15歲就做m記<br />\n已經係好好嘅工<br />\n<br />\n多得有手有腳但揾夠比自已洗就算嘅老豆<br />\n翻三個月工就休半年 <br />\n呢排仲好似長期唔返㖭<br />\n自已就係咁買大陸機 <br />\n而家好似有五部電話<br />\n我就用佢唔要嘅電話<br />\n佢連補習錢都唔肯比<br />\n仲叫我唔洗補<br />\n咁電腦 遊戲機呢啲更加唔洗諗啦<br />\n不過佢自己就買左ps3 nds psp(新出個時<br />\n不過我都未玩過<br />\n<br />\n不過好彩有我老母<br />\n佢都肯比補習錢 啱啱好夠飯錢同車錢 <br />\n同埋買手提電腦比我(愛你媽咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以 冇一定經濟水平<br />\n同冇心教好下一代嘅人<br />\n戴番個套啦 咪害人啦<br />\n下一代會同你一樣咁辛苦㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0f465f22b002c4c269ddc064ed3f87902cd450","tid":2130844,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:27:37.000Z","msg":"窮撚結紮，唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccf8ddcb72e389992ecce8cd1483baddb642b5b","tid":2130844,"uid":293677,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:29:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔止要戴套<br />\n應該要立法強制窮人絕育<br />\n窮L生仔正仆街！"},{"pid":"755040d6ae819c2b2c2d6ae9f7b0a9788a93b174","tid":2130844,"uid":312126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c0f465f22b002c4c269ddc064ed3f87902cd450","tid":2130844,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:27:37.000Z","msg":"窮撚結紮，唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:29:13.000Z","msg":"宜家上得翻u 得覺得真係呢條路好苦"},{"pid":"9dfee64315f3f33d960b617ed419f6d8e9e55f4e","tid":2130844,"uid":123020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:31:40.000Z","msg":"Asso都上番三大啦<br />\n咪玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff004d95a3fc599ddd47fee56e80cb7449bff9a","tid":2130844,"uid":129138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca95f340e636d84f2fedc0b67ee791198d69d03","tid":2130844,"uid":312126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dfee64315f3f33d960b617ed419f6d8e9e55f4e","tid":2130844,"uid":123020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:31:40.000Z","msg":"Asso都上番三大啦<br />\n咪玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:33:45.000Z","msg":"望到啲有錢人讀asso 溝女/仔<br />\n覺得自己好似同個度有啲唔襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係retake上架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}